Beazer PLC, one major British building material, and construction material, dem talk sey na 24% increase for di new financial year, na mostly money contribution wey come from U.S. unit, Koppers Co.

Taxation wey di year to June 30 increase to #142.5 million ($224.5 million) from di #114.7 million ($180.7 million) akordin to wetin di analyst yarn.

(Profet after tax, and minority gain, but before big big thing add 22% to #92.6 million from di #75.6 million wey dey di list last year, but di total money wey dey di list na 29.90 cent (47 cent) from 24.68 cent (39 cent).

